@startuml

package {
  [main] as main
  [outer] as outer
  [middle] as middle
  [inner] as inner
  [safe] as safe
}

' Normal calls
main --> outer
outer --> middle
middle --> inner

' Instrumented call
main --> safe
safe --> (exit) : call exit(0)

' Note on instrumentation
note right of safe
  <b>Инструментирована</b>
  Функция заменена на вызов
  call exit(0).
  Останавливает выполнение
  этой ветки.
end note

@enduml